.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/j-hus-burna-boy-Burak-Cingi_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/j-hus-burna-boy-Burak-Cingi_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/j-hus-burna-boy-Burak-Cingi_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/j-hus-burna-boy-Burak-Cingi_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/j-hus">J Hus</a>和<a href="/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a>已被宣布成为今年晚些时候举行的首届尼日利亚非洲国家赛的主角。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/burna-boy-live-review-london-stadium-3451830">Burna Boy 伦敦现场演出：非洲节奏主宰的历史时刻</a></li></ul><p>本月早些时候，有消息称非洲国家尼日利亚将于今年 12 月 19 日至 20 日在拉各斯塔法瓦巴莱瓦广场举行。这将是“Afro Nation”第二次在非洲举办——去年 12 月在加纳举办。</p><p>昨天（9 月 26 日），音乐节公布了 2023 年演出阵容的首批演出，确认 Burna Boy 和 J Hus 成为头条新闻。迄今为止宣布的其他名字包括非洲钻新人<a href="/artists/black-sherif">Black Sherif</a> 、高调生活歌手 Flavor 和街头流行歌星 Seyi Vibez。更多名字将在临近时间时得到确认。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxpjO7-MaZl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="d