a-braverman-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/elton-john-responds-suella-braverman-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/elton-john-responds-suella-braverman-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/elton-john-responds-suella-braverman-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/elton-john-responds-suella-braverman-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John)</a>公开反对苏埃拉·布雷弗曼 (Suella Braverman) 禁止 LGBTQ+ 寻求庇护者来到英国的呼吁。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/elton-john-glastonbury-2023-review-setlist-photos-3461062">埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的现场演出：音乐节有史以来最好的头条新闻之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>内政大臣本周面临强烈反对，因为她表示“仅仅作为同性恋或女性”不足以成为在英国获得难民身份的理由。</p><p>她周二（9 月 26 日）在美国智囊团发表讲话时（通过<em><a href="https://news.sky.com/story/inhuman-suella-braverman-condemned-by-lgbt-asylum-seekers-who-say-they-cannot-leave-uk-12970533#:~:text=LGBT%20asylum%20seekers%20in%20the,or%20to%20be%20a%20woman." target="_blank" rel="noopener">天空新闻</a></em>）说：“世界上有很多地方，成为同性恋或成为女性是极其困难的。当个人受到迫害时，我们提供庇护是正确的。</p><p> “但如果实际上只是同性恋或女性，并且担心在原籍国受到歧视就足以获得保护，我们将无法维持庇护制度。”</p><p>音乐偶像约翰现在对内政大臣作出回应，指责她“使仇恨和暴力合法化”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxqfAMEs2SS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-cont